root: ^Control, This is C3-12 Johnathan, radio check, over.
^C3-12 Johnathan, this is control, Go Ahead.
^Control, we’re under attack from within! Some creatures have escaped from their enclosures, fuck!
^Calm down, Johnathan. Do you know the cause?
^Negative! They suddenly broke free, they’re killing the crew!
^Jesus Christ, alright Johnathan, IFSE center recommends mission abort, do you concur?
^Alright, I'll try to get past these things to the escape pod.
